{"tid":237648,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB股權分佈首曝光 「中國梅鐸」黎瑞剛為最終揸Fit人","createTime":"2017-05-10T13:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T15:06:37.000Z","uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50b997b48635a1c6643665d2576b200a1204c6a8","tid":237648,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:37:07.000Z","msg":"電視廣播（TVB，511）早前宣布斥資42.09億元，以作價為每股35.075元回購股份。回購計劃觸及全購界線，最新獲證監會放行，授出清洗豁免，避過全購，但條件是要約須由大多數股東批准。<br />\n<br />\n委員會在考慮裁決時，定下要求，若最後決定授予清洗豁免，持有TVB 26%股權之大股東Young Lion，就須披露其股股權架構，及該要約的資金問題。根據最新披露Young Lion股權架構顯示，「殼王」陳國強實際只持有TVB不足2%股權，至於「中國梅鐸」黎瑞剛，則持有達兩成股份，為TVB終極大股東！<br />\n首次曝光的Young Lion股權架構如下：<br />\n●「殼王」陳國強6%（即持有約1.56% TVB）<br />\n● 由黎瑞剛主理的CMC共持有79.01%（即約20.54% TVB）；<br />\n● HTC董事長王雪紅，則透過兩家公司，共佔14.99%（即約3.90% TVB）<br />\n除Young Lion外，尚有3.9%TVB股份，由方逸華及邵氏基金持有。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170510/large/1494408424_c37c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170510%2Flarge%2F1494408424_c37c.jpg&h=32a75498&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdaa6575a2cd7050079ed226e86a4a501ed22367","tid":237648,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:43:14.000Z","msg":"黎瑞剛, 中共黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1db8664593b39c8e9df4890dd9307707e027440","tid":237648,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢中國梅毒話？"},{"pid":"edec997a2f19043cb93d20f37942cb5c7c60eacd","tid":237648,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"滲晒染晒紅 冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbf2f9f48ebead1692d9116e7f99b9f47908126","tid":237648,"uid":56926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:13:07.000Z","ms